" Neovim の :terminal でも水平・上下分割で開けるようにする
" cf. https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/5073
if has('nvim')
  command! -nargs=* Term rightbelow new | set nonumber | terminal <args>
  command! -nargs=* Termv vsplit | terminal <args>
endif

